name: Lava-skin Maneki
description:
High-res artwork of Maneki Gang #13001, originally minted by x1sMIND on the Ethereum blockchain

The Maneki Gang NFT Collection is a top quality profile picture art with over 180 hand-drawn features spread across 8 layers resulting in an unsurpassed variety and uniqueness.

Modeled after a Japanese lucky cat, these beautiful artworks live on the Ethereum blockchain in the form of ERC-721 tokens. In addition to the high-resolution artwork copyright of which is fully granted to the token holder, each Maneki Gang grants access to benefits found on the Lucky Maneki website and Discord.
